nodes.text: Newenurf was a location in the galaxy. It was the homeworld of private guard Prod. The Sqra Castle was located on Newenurf.

Newenurf was introduced in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
